betterquesting:10.desc:8:
If you've gotten this far, you already know what these multis are about, and probably built at least a dozen of them. That said, there are about a dozen more with varying levels of usefulness.

Unfortunately, the tiering of a GT++ multi doesn't always say how powerful it is. It is in our best interest that new multis are placed in good spots throughout progression, but there is a lot of old baggage that hasn't stood the test of time.

As a committed GTNH engineer, you can help uncover the true extent of what GT++ has to offer. You ought not to stop!
